t:
‘I love you.’
                                              •••
“That meant everything to me. You were the only one who always knew and didn't ignore me and I knew it wouldn't happen without you. Now I wonder if I've done something wrong. I've moved on and I don't really care about what happens. You've done well and I don't mind if you have a relationship with someone else. But I'm not going to look for you, not now that you're lost to me.”
c:
#humanAIcollaboration: In the human-AI collaboration, I take a prompt and feed it through an AI. The AI writes the story and I add the final touches to make it more presentable and understandable. These stories might not make sense but just know that a computer wrote these.



#love #breakup #moveon
Here's a #collab prompt for #YoStoWriMo. Write a first person story titled #dontaskmeout which reads like a letter to someone who likes you but you don't feel the same way.

Post longer pieces in the caption.   #YourQuoteAndMine
Collaborating with YourQuote Baba
